Algebraic rules have indices disabled.

Assignment and rate rules determine which indices are enabled using the type over the variable.  Namely, if the variable is scaler, both disabled.  If vector, row index enabled, if matrix both enabled.

Listener on Type and Variable need to update the enabledness of these.



